main event: A sighting of a luminous object was reported at Sampson Air Force Base, New York on January 26, 1953.
interesting points: The object was described as large, rectangular in shape and was observed for about one minute,It emitted a humming sound while moving,The object traveled through an arc of 70 or 80 degrees,The sighting was reported by multiple military personnel at the base,The conclusion drawn from the sighting indicated it could be a probable aircraft.
sighted object: luminous rectangular shaped unidentified flying object
witness description: military personnel at Sampson Air Force Base
